+  "title": "ExecuteMsg",
+  "description": "The incentives execute message surface that downstream consumers may drive. Admin-side mutations (`UpdateConfig`, `RemoveRewardFromPool`, `ClaimOrphanedRewards`, `UpdateBlockedTokenslist`, ownership transfer, `DeactivatePool`, `DeactivateBlockedPools`) are NOT mirrored.",
+  "oneOf": [
